We will predict future financial values using a recursive approach. Assume the future value is calculated using the formula:

FV=PV×(1+r)^n

 
Where:
FV: Future Value

PV: Present Value

r: Growth rate per period

n: Number of periods

Using recursion:

Base case: When 
n=0, 

𝐹𝑉=𝑃𝑉

Recursive case: 

𝐹𝑉(𝑛)=𝐹𝑉(𝑛−1)×(1+𝑟)
